wanted creator marketing that drove neighborhood-first foot traffic. The community responded — Bed-Stuy now has some of Push's strongest engagement metrics in Brooklyn. Campaigns here work because they're built on trust: creators who live in the neighborhood, documenting businesses they actually support."}]]}]}],"$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb"]}]],["$Lc","$Ld"],"$Le"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"jP0DLMf4-wLgFORDq_Yoq"}
